td.div: English: Flag of Iraq. Sources claim that this is a temporary flag, and is likely to be changed in the future. The writing says allahu akbar (see en:Takbir).

td.p: This image is based on a previous version of Image:Flag of Iraq.svg and has been compared and cross-checked with cia factbook, by User:Militaryace - Modifed Arabic script to reflect the current format used by the Iraqi Government. (visit Office of the President of Iraq for comparison.) [File Updated October 2008 - updated Kufic script.]
Authored by User:Militaryace based on the work of User:Hoshie
